  <h1>Ecosystem Timeline</h1>

  <section>
    <p>
      This page records the dated public artifacts produced by the AEGIS Initiative
      since the project's inception. Every entry references a verifiable
      source — a Git tag, a published release, a Zenodo DOI, or a public
      submission. The timeline is maintained as an evidentiary record of the
      ecosystem's development and is updated as new artifacts ship.
    </p>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section>
    <h2>Origin (January–February 2026)</h2>
    <ul>
      <li><strong>2026-01-26</strong> — Project conceived.</li>
      <li><strong>2026-02-04</strong> — First commit.</li>
      <li>
        <strong>2026-02-25</strong> — <a href="https://github.com/aegis-initiative/aegis-constitution">aegis-constitution</a>
        repository initialized; initial constitutional structure committed.
      </li>
    </ul>
  </section>

  <hr />

  <section>
    <h2>Foundation (March 2026)</h2>
    <p>
      The architecture is laid down across all three layers of the ecosystem —
      constitution, governance specifications, and runtime — and the first
      cited artifacts are deposited.
    </p>
    <ul>
      <li>
        <strong>2026-03-05</strong> — <a href="https://github.com/aegis-initiative/aegis-governance/releases/tag/v0.1.0">aegis-governance v0.1.0</a>
        published: first public release of the governance framework.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>2026-03-06</strong> — <a href="https://github.com/aegis-initiative/aegis-governance/releases/tag/v0.1.1">aegis-governance v0.1.1</a>.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>2026-03-07</strong> — <a href="/research/papers/">NIST AI Risk
        Management Framework position statement</a> submitted.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>2026-03-08</strong> — Ecosystem expansion: <a href="https://github.com/aegis-initiative/aegis-core">aegis-core</a>,
        <a href="https://github.com/aegis-initiative/aegis-initiative">aegis-initiative</a>,
        <a href="https://github.com/aegis-initiative/aegis-docs">aegis-docs</a>,
        <a href="https://github.com/aegis-initiative/aegis-sdk">aegis-sdk</a>,
        <a href="https://github.com/aegis-initiative/aegis-federation">aegis-federation</a>,
        and <a href="https://github.com/aegis-initiative/aegis-labs">aegis-labs</a>
        repositories initialized in a single coordinated batch.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>2026-03-19</strong> — <a href="https://github.com/aegis-initiative/aegis-constitution/releases/tag/v0.1.1">aegis-constitution v0.1.1</a>.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>2026-03-21</strong> — <a href="https://github.com/aegis-initiative/aegis-constitution/releases/tag/v0.2.0">aegis-constitution v0.2.0</a>.
      </li>
      <li>
        <strong>2026-03-22</strong> — Constitution adopts calendar versioning
        (<a href="https://github.com/aegis-initiative/aegis-constitution/releases/tag/v26.3.22">v26.3.22</a>);
